template.name: Template SNMP Watchdog
template.description: Template based on Geist SuperGoose II (Watchdog 1250) v3.15.0 via SNMP.

item.name: Temperature Precision
item.description: Temperature Precision: 0 =degree:whole degree (value X 1) 1 =deci-degree:tenths of a degree (value X 10) ex. 550 =55.0 degrees

discovery_rule.name: WatchDog Climate Devices Discovery
discovery_rule.description: We are searching for Climate Devices accessible via SNMP interface. In my case there is only one Climate Device therefore this Discovery is not necessary. But it could be useful for the next versions of GEIST Watchdog devices

trigger_prototype.name: {#WDSNMPCLINM} temp F is higher CRIT level {$CRIT_TEMP_F}
trigger_prototype.description: CRITICAL trigger for Temp in F. You can change warning level by changing {$CRIT_TEMP_F} macro.

trigger_prototype.name: {#WDSNMPCLINM} Temp is raising (more then 5 F during last 10 min)
trigger_prototype.description: The temperature has been rising (or falling) fast. (More than 5 F during last 10 minutes.)
